race.comment: Plenty of speedy types here so looking for one that might be running on if they overdo it up front. Victorian visitor MY ZEPHYR (10) is lightly raced but she's got some ability. Her recent trial was good and she looks ready for a big first-up run. Todd Pannell is a great booking for her. TRULY ELSA (4) is a speedy type that is also first-up and has also trialed well. Suspect she will go forward and be in the firing line. She can tough it out and finish in the money. CARARADA (5) is first-up and, while she typically takes a run or two to hit her straps, she's another that can be running on if the tempo is hot. STARLITE VALLEY (1) and REFRESHING (3) are both very quick and could lead this. REFRESHING has really found her mojo of late but this is harder.
